GENSYMCID-1848 - "Write regression test for GENSYMCID-1697"
Essense of regression is that there is a self-connected object O with connection C in a subworkspace of object S. When S is cloned, connection on a subworkspace used to disappear. We use several queries to ensure that after cloning:
- clone of O exists (let's name it O') - O' is connected to a single connection C' of appropriate class - O' is the only object connected to C' - O' is self-connected via C'
